date\u202fC best satisfies the core criteria with the least critical gaps. Unless new evidence emerges showing that Candidate\u202fB is reliably safe and a strong team player, Candidate\u202fC should be selected.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
